      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient.DbClientOptions",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient.DbClientOptions.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Process-wide knobs for <code>Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient</code>. Settings here are read\nfrom the global Dapper type-map delegate that <code>ColumnAttributeTypeMapper</code>\ninstalls, so they affect read-side column resolution only.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient.DbColumnAttribute.yml",
      "output": {
