      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient.DbExtractor<TRecord>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient.DbExtractor-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Extracts records from a database query as an asynchronous stream.\nUses Dapper for column-to-property mapping, supporting <code>[Column]</code> attribute\nand convention-based name matching.</p>\n"
    },
