      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient.DbTableAttribute",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.DbClient.DbTableAttribute.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Marks a record / class as mapping to a database table. Triggers the\nWolfgang.Etl.DbClient source generator to emit a partial class with\nreflection-free <code>Insert</code> SQL + parameter-binding helpers.</p>\n"
